SourceForge
===========
EffecTV project page is opened at SourceForge(http://sourceforge.net/).

http://sourceforge.net/projects/effectv/

Some resources for collaborative work is available.

Mailing list
------------
If you want to subscribe EffecTV crews mailing list, read the description
at http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listrinfo/effectv-developers.

Discussion forum
----------------
There are three open discussion forum, "Help", "Effects coders forum" and
"Open discussion".

Help
	Questions and problems should be posted here.
Effects coders forum
	Discussion space for effects coders.
Open Discussion
	Free discussion space.

CVS
---
CVS repository of EffecTV can be checked out from project page. A short
description for CVS access can be found at there.

If you want to access as a developer, you should be the member of EffecTV
developers group. Please ask me to join to developers group.

